{"tid":1438082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"｛勿忘初衷，五大訴求，不割蓆，不分化｝對家出招不外乎分化，而且層面比以往更深","createTime":"2019-08-09T16:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T17:07:28.000Z","uid":66828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e9dcf8358f56bc76a353063ad4b693ab773c69c6","tid":1438082,"uid":66828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:33:42.000Z","msg":"由開頭，<br />\n黃絲 &lt;&gt; 藍絲<br />\n警察 &lt;&gt; 人民(呢個係必經階段，贏到黑警就贏政府)<br />\n勇武 &lt;&gt; 和理非<br />\n<br />\n以往係比較單純，直接既分化，但我地經過14年洗禮，不奏效<br />\n<br />\n所以手法比以往升級左，但其實都係歸去最當初既對立:<br />\n黑警做戲 ，洗白 &gt; 籠絡中立，淺黃 &gt; 藍黃對立<br />\n4點鐘記招 &gt; 洗腦，鞏固淺藍，籠絡中立 &gt; 藍黃對立<br />\n左膠 &gt; 譴責暴力 &gt; 勇武和理非對立<br />\n黑社會 &gt; 警黑合作 &gt; 警察鬥人民<br />\n大台 &gt; 分化現場陣線 &gt; 勇武和理非對立<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府所有既招數，萬變不離其宗，都係打算內部瓦解我地<br />\n而分化亦都係共產黨最擅長既招數!!!  </span></span><br />\n因為濫捕嚇唔到我地，唔可以出解放軍<br />\n所以會有更多各式各樣既分化<br />\n5毛會愈來愈多<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得我地當初721元朗之後係點做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係入去踩平佢!!!</span></span><br />\n我地同班牛屎佬講，我地香港人唔係好蝦既<br />\n<br />\n要贏呢場運動，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地一定要團結一致，齊上，直到勝利一刻!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記著我地當初五大訴求<br />\n記著我地要繼續做文宣，籠絡更多人<br />\n記著我地要be humble, 因為我地要招攬更多有志之士<br />\n記著我地不割蓆，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武放核彈都不割!!! 和理非罷買，罷交稅，罷工罷到經濟崩潰都不割!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時代革命!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95aae2192f33e7073ec68b362f2abaa0174a1fe3","tid":1438082,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:37:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同我推一千萬次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ffe9ee3b5e8451b883425ade2afa4ec2d4ce9259","tid":1438082,"uid":66828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95aae2192f33e7073ec68b362f2abaa0174a1fe3","tid":1438082,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:37:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同我推一千萬次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:40:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b898a02701fdae3e72e32841d72078a207ee9ec2","tid":1438082,"uid":66828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:55:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a2c8df38af14f2bc29887a423147fee9eca57f5","tid":1438082,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pr7bDZj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpr7bDZj.jpg&h=3c76ee61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3NAgP50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3NAgP50.jpg&h=4f346020&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/014Ju50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F014Ju50.jpg&h=f64410ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9nZNVs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9nZNVs.jpg&h=f20d701e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6903c0d321a2